      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis validation against FDA pump geometry — 2025 Q3 experimental campaign",
      "description": "Experimental hemolysis index measurements collected September 2025 across 5 flow-speed operating points. CFD predictions compared against measured NIH values. Mean absolute error 18.3%. Dataset vintage 2025-09-30 predates the February 2026 model revision; re-validation against revised mesh topology and updated power-law hemolysis coefficients is planned for Q2 2026 but not yet executed."
    },
