      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/uncertainty-quantification-2026q1",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification — hemolysis index predictions",
      "description": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on hemolysis predictions using 1000 samples of inlet boundary conditions and blood viscosity parameters. 95th-percentile hemolysis index remains below clinical threshold at 4 of 5 operating points. One operating point at maximum speed shows marginal exceedance of 3.2%."
    }
  ],
