      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between experimental conditions and CFD boundary conditions demonstrating equivalence within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency assessment between experimental and simulation input parameters not formally completed. Informal comparison suggests flow rates match within 4% and rotational speeds within 1%, but a structured equivalency matrix covering all boundary conditions has not been produced. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 2 by default; required level 4 not met."
    }
