    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model for VAD use with conditions. Seven of thirteen credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels; six factors carry epistemic gaps. The primary experimental validation dataset (dataVintage 2025-09-30) predates the model revision of 2026-02-14; re-validation against the updated model build is planned for Q2 2026 and is a binding condition of this acceptance. Monte Carlo UQ confirms hemolysis predictions remain below clinical threshold at 4 of 5 operating points. Conditional acceptance is granted pending completion of re-validation and resolution of discretization error (GCI 11.7% vs. 5% target).",
